      "name": "COU2 operating envelope: VAD flow and speed bounds",
      "description": "Operating envelope spans five flow-speed combinations: flow rates from 3.0 L/min to 7.0 L/min (±0.1 L/min measurement uncertainty) and pump speeds from 2000 RPM to 3500 RPM (±25 RPM). Inlet pressure boundary: 5–15 mmHg. Outlet pressure: 60–120 mmHg. Blood temperature: 37 °C ± 1 °C. Hematocrit: 35–42%. All five operating points lie strictly within the validated flow-speed space; no extrapolation is invoked."
    }
